{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act17side", "eventName": "愚人號", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SN-ST-7", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "宴會廳", "storyInfo": "斯圖提斐拉號上獵人們無法與阿方索達成共識，小鎮上的深海教徒和鎮民也不可能與審判庭和解。矛盾根深蒂固，亟需解決。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"screenadapt": "coverall", "image": "bg_ibbar", "width": 1.0, "height": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你回來了。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你的付出，我知道，對於你而言，違背信仰仍然是一件痛苦的事情。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是美好就在前方。這絕非虛妄的允諾，而是實際的救贖。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝你。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡門閣下深不可測，欺騙他沒有多大意義。他很快就會發現真相。", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也該謝謝蒂亞戈。我們撒這個謊，意味著他一定會死，死在審判庭手裡。", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我沒見過海洋的使者，但傳言，使者不會拒絕同族的要求。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為同族的選擇一定有利於族群，同族的想法一定是族群的想法。我們應當學習，這也是其中一環。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就讓蒂亞戈自己去愁吧。", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你在擔心。沒必要。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的先知，阿瑪雅小姐，她真的還能回來嗎？", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只是選擇先我們一步回歸海洋，為了尋找道途、使者，和沉睡城市的蹤跡。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她回來，是為了接濟同胞，她一去不返，也只是為了未來做著準備。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不必為她擔心，我們只要知道，阿瑪雅小姐不希望審判庭過多地關注到她，無論她身在何方。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那這個人，伊比利亞人，我們抓來做什麼？", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#3$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的女主人似乎和那位卡門達成了某種協議。他是敵人。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......真希望你別用這樣的稱呼描述我和醫生的關係。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#4$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直在調查我們，不是嗎？", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我花費了不少時間，向你闡述我們的真理，我們不想傷害你。你想明白了嗎？", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想我對你們的偽善已經很明白了，不需要多說啦。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......偽善？哦......你還在談論道德，人世的道德。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先不論海嗣恐魚這些玩意究竟算什麼，我看到的是一群對伊比利亞和審判庭心存不滿，然後找了各種藉口想要加害審判庭的壞傢伙。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是個伊比利亞人，雖然我在伊比利亞生活的時間不算特別長......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我去過很多地方，見過很多事情，你們這樣的人其實很多，還總覺得自己特別。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們說的神是真的，就，呃，什麼進化的崇高，生命的極致——", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——那你們的神一定對你們這樣的人不屑一顧吧？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——！", "name": "冷靜的鎮民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_461_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，你說得對。所以使者斷絕了聯繫，只有先知阿瑪雅能夠聽見海的言語，向我們傳達指令。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（阿瑪雅果然有問題......嘖，怎麼就沒早點抓到證據呢。）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不過......）", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#9$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......情況怎麼樣？", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的那些，溟痕，根本靠近不了城鎮的核心區域。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那隻黑色的怪物不僅會飛，還會噴吐可怕的熱流，溟痕蔓延的速度完全趕不上它燒毀的速度。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再拖下去，等那些阻攔懲戒軍的恐魚全軍覆沒，格蘭法洛就會落入審判庭的手裡。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都會死。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，蒂亞戈，不。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在談論那些......為了拖延敵人腳步而自願犧牲的同胞時，你並不悲傷。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換言之，你也沒做好隨時為族群犧牲的準備。", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這樣和我說話，我們只是利害一致。我對擁抱海洋不感興趣，我已經是一把老骨頭了。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......冥頑不化的低級生物......", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彼此。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你，年輕人，我早說了，你別多管閒事。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂亞戈，你......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#5$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們互相認識？", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。只是有一個總坐在禮拜堂的外鄉人，我身為這裡的鎮長，總有印象的。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不該多管閒事。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也該有所動作了吧？難道要等著審判官和他那個帶著怪物的同謀把我的小鎮燒個精光？", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會。你真是執著於這個小鎮，為什麼？", "name": "古怪的教徒"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_453_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蘭法洛是我們幾代人重建伊比利亞願景的縮影，異教徒，你問問那些加入你們的本地人，你會明白的。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審判庭毀了足夠多的東西，我要他們加倍償還。", "name": "蒂亞戈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_451_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g22_goldenboat_hall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "fadetime": 3.0, "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#2"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是斯卡蒂，不是伊莎瑪拉。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#2"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那伊莎瑪拉這個發音意味著什麼？", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#9"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#9"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂知道，斯卡蒂不敢回答。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭告訴過她沒事，她願意相信。"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這只是一種逃避。她知道這個稱呼意味著什麼。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意味著深淵裡的巨響。血肉摩擦著岩壁下墜，唯有意志攀高直上，衝破海洋。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "意味著那場鏖戰之後，留在了自己體內的某些，“東西”。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcave", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_186"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的血與你的血相同。", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聞到我們氣味，正如我們聞見你氣味。", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們找到我們，殺死我們......", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不懂時，我們也殺死你們。", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們餵養海洋。我們的屍體供養了海洋。", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Ishar-mla，我們擁有同個故鄉。", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g22_goldenboat_hall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "審判官！你怎麼膽敢與她們為伍？！", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#3$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什、什麼？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，滾下我的船！否則你會和那隻一樣，成為這一輪狩獵的獵物！", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#3$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢著，船長先生。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您又是怎麼知道......這個名字的呢？", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來告訴你為什麼，吞食這些血肉改變著我們的軀體，我親手處決了三位數的倖存者，直到最後。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在是我提問，你體內也流著它們的血，我能聞到。而且你一定比其他人更特別。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_263_skadi#8"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼鬼話——", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "char_263_skadi#8"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看我的手。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯卡蒂向下看去。"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船長的一隻手已經成為了海嗣的形狀，新生的蹼膜透明可見，觸鬚狀的延伸正不斷抽搐搖擺。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在努力克制什麼。看得出來，這隻手上的東西正在干擾船長的軀體。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它在渴求著我的思維，讓我解救你，讓我向你傾訴，讓我聆聽你的想法。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "立刻滾出我的船。否則我會連你們一起殺死。殺死你才能保證我身為人類的清醒——滾！", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——我們付出了這麼大的犧牲才來到這裡，如果你真的還留有伊比利亞英雄的意識，你就應該與我們合作！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#4$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......仔細想想，小審判官。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在這裡苦苦掙扎的時間已經遠超我在家鄉征戰的時日。你能理解什麼？", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幽閉一年就可以摧垮人的意志，你知道我們花了多少年和海浪調情？", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "七八年前，我親手處決了最後一個船員並把他扔進了海裡。他保持著人類的意志死去，他是最後一個。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那些伊比利亞最好的水手、戰士、信念堅定的科學家，他們在這艘船上最常見的死法是，自殺。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你無法想像我的經歷，我的左半身奪走了我的夢境，我不需要睡眠，這是一種折磨。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在這漫長的折磨中，我唯一能做的，就是不斷獵殺那些大大小小的怪物，然後花時間，清潔，我的船。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我和我的大副待在一起，回你們該去的地方。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不屬於你們，也不屬於海洋，我只屬於我的伊比利亞，“愚人號”。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g23_goldenboat_pass", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌蕾蒂婭停下腳步。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在思考這裡為何如此乾淨整潔的同時，也留意到了氣息的變化。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣。這裡當然有海嗣。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，這種不純粹的氣味是什麼緣故？以及，自己始終感受到的，隱隱的預感又來自何方？"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只能繼續走著，按照腦海裡記下的路線，試圖抵達這艘船的深處。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然間，她停下了腳步。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......在這艘六十餘年未曾靠岸的原始運輸工具上，您是否顯得過於突兀？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深海主教。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "fadetime": 3.0, "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您能一眼識破，是不是因為我露面的地點不太好？", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你跟著我們來的。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，要說先後順序的話，可是我先回到這艘船上的。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#3$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海洋與我交流，海洋接納我，海洋幫助我。從一開始，抵達這艘船於我而言就並非難事。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#4$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您按捺住上前殺死我的衝動，這很了不起。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是因為您覺得，這艘船對您的宏遠計畫至關重要嗎？", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想要什麼？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您殺死了昆圖斯。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼不知道，你們這些無趣的實驗垃圾——請原諒——也會替同伴復仇？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，您誤會了。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昆圖斯稍顯急於求成，而他的這一脾性，不僅導致了他的失敗，更是他仍舊生而為人的證明。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可這沒什麼可恥的。用我們的方式思考，只是思考，永遠無法成為我們想成為的。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“唯有血肉與神經的變化才是真實的。”你說對嗎，深海獵人？", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們沒必要為敵。我什麼也不會做。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結局在生命誕生的那一刻就已經延伸至此，沒有什麼能改變這一事實。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只是為了講幾句廢話，就費這麼大勁跟到海洋上來？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關於這個嘛......", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您還不必知道。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fish_howl"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_457_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_457_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些低劣的生物擋不住我。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$tactfulboost", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.3, "g": 0.3, "b": 5.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿瑪雅嫣然一笑，沒有回答。藍色的光芒在她的腳下浮現，很快籠罩了整片走廊。"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“溟痕”。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......格蘭法洛的溟痕，那些陷阱，是你的手筆。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。你們總是將一切禍事歸咎於深海教會，卻不願思考這一切現象背後的真理。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些孩子在更久以前就存在於格蘭法洛。我只是......找到它們而已。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，無所謂。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是海的中央，肉眼不可見的觸碰無處不在。這艘船，對你們回歸阿戈爾，也許幫助不大。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過您真打算回阿戈爾嗎？您真沒有半點心思......去聽一聽使者們的話？", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你和那個愚蠢的主教沒什麼區別。你甚至沒有像樣地戰鬥過，否則，你就不會對一個獵人說出這種蠢話。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。也不是所有獵人，都把傲慢甘之如飴。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再會了，歌蕾蒂婭。你讓我有些遺憾，不過無妨，也許有一個突破口就是好的。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但決定你們去留的，決定阿戈爾去留的，不會是我。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#6$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼可能從我面前離開？", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#2$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_456_1#1$1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$b_char_mon3terdieroar_phase2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（刺耳尖嘯）——！！", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_456_1#1$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昆圖斯的身邊應當還有一位使者。您與那位使者廝殺，您與那位使者對話。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們停滯不前，海洋從未停止。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想遏制進化，那阿戈爾，還不夠聰明。", "name": "阿瑪雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_449_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站住！", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#2"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_458_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Gla-dia......", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_458_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會說話的弱小獵物，倒確實更接近畜生。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早些死去吧，我好去找那個主教算帳。我有話要問她。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g22_goldenboat_hall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "fadetime": 3.0, "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$b_char_mon3terdieroar_phase2", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——你聽見了嗎，大副？獵物發出嘶鳴，它在呼喚我們。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#2$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_452_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被稱作大副的怪物微微點頭，頭冠險些滑落，它用爪去扶正。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它在嘶鳴，它在呼喚我們——你們還有其他同夥！？", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#3$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是劍魚......", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一定發現了什麼。這裡的氣味並不尋常，只是海風迷惑了我們。", "name": "幽靈鯊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1023_ghost2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真高興它沒有被這幾個骯髒的阿戈爾人嚇走，我們已經嬉鬧了數月有餘，我可不希望它再破壞船體了。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#9$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "狩獵......是說，狩獵那隻海嗣嗎？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_4009_irene_1#2$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海嗣？......（沙啞的笑聲）是的。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#9$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在生存的土地上狩獵果腹，亙古以來人們就是這麼做的。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#9$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐘聲再次敲響的時候，你們還沒走，你們就死。", "name": "船長阿方索"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_452_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_446_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}